{"tid":1249091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術] 發夢夢見好有成效 五六個人組個小隊","createTime":"2019-06-21T15:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:02:59.000Z","uid":207441,"like":130,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f147b9461471b103debda23342d9ba1dadcd8d","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"雖然好似好普通，但其實好緊要<br />\n<br />\n發夢時5-6人小隊 <span style=\"color: pink;\">搬鐵馬，推水箱 行動十分迅速地完成路障建設</span>，多謝今日願意配合既bro<br />\n<br />\n任何行動既時候最好搵多一兩組人 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五六個人一組</span><br />\n無論如何都痴埋一齊 小隊形式行動<br />\n行動時<span style=\"color: pink;\">更有信心、把握同有後援</span><br />\n有目標行動自然更見效 例如搬物資同集合 <br />\n小隊<span style=\"color: orange;\">又方便分清邊個係自己人 </span><br />\n而且資訊方便流通 免得有人洛單<br />\n單走係好危險 而且執行力未必高<br />\n<br />\n小隊的話有事都叫做有個關照 同埋以後想行動都方便call番出黎<br />\n<br />\n同埋今日想講既係，叫人唔好影相係岩，保障大家，但態度要好，因為我地需要集合更多民意，我地唔係狗我地要理性進行運動，只要多一個市民認同我地佢地就可能叫埋朋友一齊支持，畢竟香港人太少抗爭，我地要凝聚更加多基礎嘅民意同力量先可以成功，溫文提點佢地唔可以影相，我地就比較會得民心，反之亦然，被添上爛仔，搞亂社會之惡名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">最後⋯<br />\n香港人加油啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(p.s. 我講緊夢話)"},{"pid":"84bef2a747e282f02571d6c917e5735fbb284f76","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd862c5d910fbba3fd720deb4a3becdec72a9e6","tid":1249091,"uid":258291,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"同埋今日想講既係，叫人唔好影相係岩，保障大家，但態度要好，因為我地需要集合更多民意，我地唔係狗我地要理性進行運動，只要多一個市民認同我地佢地就可能叫埋朋友一齊支持，畢竟香港人太少抗爭，我地要凝聚更加多基礎嘅民意同力量先可以成功，溫文提點佢地唔可以影相，我地就比較會得民心，反之亦然，被添上爛仔，搞亂社會之惡名<br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322fa7f98beefee6f64556c44e651f309e01ab59","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊 加油啊 今日大家都好齊心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52154026bf097238e556a65fecd7c10e7fb9fdb","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!"},{"pid":"cb66c9420ffa2ba880a84fc5baac92f680c767e4","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"我知依家仲有好多人單緊機架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44b5f8f74b7c169ecec4f4095cf56e0a1a3a6ed","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"到時去現場搵下啲單機既朋友組隊五排啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61ae998eaced9397ed3a10325c4a0a7462e1820","tid":1249091,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"發夢見到5,6個人連鐵欄都搬得郁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4461f29528571c5515c851f0096543cb3f5b6052","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!! 同意請推po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9ebec70c1212a0a487b0019de63e8f50613481","tid":1249091,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44b5f8f74b7c169ecec4f4095cf56e0a1a3a6ed","tid":1249091,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"到時去現場搵下啲單機既朋友組隊五排啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"好多都3 4個人<br />\n單丁唔敢埋堆 人地又驚鬼"},{"pid":"ec40563a58a3082